{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id77825e00-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s410eeee–10"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"410eeee–10"},"text":"§ 410eeee–10.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Class I or class II redesignation for clean air purposes","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For the purposes of part C of the Clean Air Act [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s7470"},"text":"42 U.S.C. 7470","children":[],"tail":" et seq.], the State may redesignate the national river only as class I or class II."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id77825e01-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/95/625/tXI/s1111"},"text":"Pub. L. 95–625, title XI, § 1111","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1978-11-10"},"text":"Nov. 10, 1978","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/92/3548"},"text":"92 Stat. 3548","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id77825e02-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id77825e03-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id77825e04-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Clean Air Act, referred to in text, is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1955-07-14/ch360"},"text":"act July 14, 1955, ch. 360","children":[],"tail":", as amended generally by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/88/206"},"text":"Pub. L. 88–206","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1963-12-17"},"text":"Dec. 17, 1963","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/77/392"},"text":"77 Stat. 392","children":[],"tail":", and later by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/95/95"},"text":"Pub. L. 95–95","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1977-08-07"},"text":"Aug. 7, 1977","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/91/685"},"text":"91 Stat. 685","children":[],"tail":". The Clean Air Act was originally classified to chapter 15B (§ 1857 et seq.) of Title 42, The Public Health and Welfare. On enactment of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/95/95"},"text":"Pub. L. 95–95","children":[],"tail":", the Act was reclassified to chapter 85 (§ 7401 et seq.) of Title 42. Part C of the Clean Air Act is classified generally to part C (§ 7470 et seq.) of subchapter I of chapter 85 of Title 42. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s7401"},"text":"section 7401 of Title 42","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"id77825e05-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section was formerly classified to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s460m–24"},"text":"section 460m–24 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
